# üîí IMPORTANT SECURITY REMINDERS
# ==========================================================
#
# ‚úÖ DO:
# - Use HTTPS URLs only (never http://)
# - Use public keys only (pk_*, EXPO_PUBLIC_*)
# - Route sensitive operations through Edge Functions
# - Keep this file in version control as a template
#
# ‚ùå DON'T:
# - Add API keys (OpenAI, HuggingFace, USDA secret keys)
# - Use localhost, 127.0.0.1, or 10.0.2.2
# - Include secret keys (sk_*, rk_*, secret_*)
# - Commit your actual .env file (only .env.example)
#
# ==========================================================
# üèóÔ∏è EDGE FUNCTIONS HANDLE SECURE OPERATIONS
# ==========================================================
#
# The following operations are securely handled server-side:
# - OpenAI API calls (GPT-4, Vision, Embeddings)
# - HuggingFace model inference
# - USDA FoodData Central API
# - Stripe payment processing
# - Email sending
# - Database operations with sensitive data
# - Any operation requiring secret keys
